ces back into standard Arriva branding. <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.arrivabus.co.uk/hinckleybus/|title=Services in Hinckley}}</ref>\n\n==Services==\nArriva operate most of their services around Leicester from either [[Haymarket Bus Station, Leicester|Haymarket]] or [[St Margaret's Bus Station]]s with a number of services operating from on-street stops within the city centre.\n\n==Depots==\nArriva operates from four depots across Leicestershire in [[Barwell, Leicestershire|Barwell]] , [[Hugglescote]], [[South Wigston]] and [[Thurmaston, Leicestershire|Thurmaston]] which is the headquarters for [[Arriva Midlands]] \n\nThe Barwell depot is also the base for [[ArrivaClick]] services in Leicester.\n\n==Fleet==\nAs of March 2014 the fleet consisted of 200+ vehicles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Fleet list|url=http://www.ukbuses.co.uk/fleet/arriva_midlands.pdf|accessdate=2 March 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130822061548/http://ukbuses.co.uk/fleet/arriva_midlands.pdf|archive-date=22 August 2013|url-status=dead}}</ref> \n\n==See also==\n*[[List of bus operators of the United Kingdom]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Arriva Fox County}}\n{{Commons category|Midland (bus company)}}\n*[http://www.arrivabus.co.uk/Midlands/ Arriva Midlands website]\n\n{{Arriva Group UK}}\n{{Bus companies in the East Midlands}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2011}}\n\n[[Category:Arriva Group bus operators in England|Fox County]]\n[[Category:Transport in Leicestershire]]\n[[Category:Bus operators in Leicestershire]]\n", "name_user": "YTRK", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arriva_Fox_County"}
